    public class BlockingSensorReadingQueue
extends java.util.concurrent.ArrayBlockingQueue<SensorReading>
    This class is a blocking queue of sensor readings. It defines a queue of capacity QUEUE_CAPACITY containing sensor readings that will be sent to the server.
